「历史修正主义」。 「他们公然的不道德（行为）是显而易见的：若没有苏联战胜纳粹德国，波兰这个作为波兰人民的民族国家就不会存在，数百万波兰人将面临被纳粹分子奴役和消灭的悲惨命运。」佳普金说。 俄卫星社称，波兰政府此前表示，他们要求德国赔偿 6.2 万亿兹罗提（兹罗提是波兰货币，约合 9.2 万亿元人民币），作为对二战造成的损失的赔偿。与此同时，波兰政客多次表示，他们不仅希望得到德国的赔偿，还希望得到俄罗斯的战争赔偿。（环球网）俄外交部官员：波兰向俄罗斯索要二战赔偿是政治幻想"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-cc75a50b35414eaec29190f789d0e5a2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/558083163"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyOvZ8NHBpZZ4EAMaCDg2MzAxNDI2IL+v/pkGMBM4lwFALnIJNTU4MDgzMTYzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1665163659.4527566", "card_id": "Q_557853408", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "圈外人，好奇哪类画师才不会被未来 ai 作画取代？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-0f17d37ea733ec0e1a3bf0ed7df624cd_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/557853408"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IyOvZ8NHBpZZ4EAMaCDg2MjUwMzE3IOjV9pkGMAA4eEAvcgk1NTc4NTM0MDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1665163659.453267", "card_id": "Q_321633612", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2182}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你听过领导说过最让你遍体生寒的话是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在工作中，会遇到各种各样的领导，而领导对下属的训话，有教导的，亲切的，当然也有些让人听了遍体生寒的。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-072180b043c488b7a8680706b0c7a78e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/321633612"}}, "